Description: RPM Development Tools
 rpmdevtools provides several utilities for RPM package development,
 including rpmdev-bumpspec, rpmdev-diff, rpmdev-extract, rpmdev-newspec,
 rpmdev-setuptree, rpmdev-spectool, rpmdev-vercmp, and others.
 .
 This package includes shell scripts and Python scripts for working
 with RPM spec files, source archives, and RPM version comparison.
